히든메뉴 외 apps 컴파일방법 
1.  
vi vendor/kaon/Android.mk 
# Apps 
include $(LOCAL_PATH)/apps/Android.mk 
# Porting Layer API HAL 
# include $(LOCAL_PATH)/hals/Android.mk 
# For prebuilt 
#include $(LOCAL_PATH)/prebuilts/Android.mk 
1-1. KaonHiddenMenu 디렉토리 삭제 또는 다른곳으로 이동 
2.  
source build/envsetup.sh 
3. 
lunch K1100UA_bkouc500-userdebug 
4.  
mmm vendor/kaon/apps/KaonManagerService/
mmm vendor/kaon/apps/KaonCmAutoUpgrade/
mmm vendor/kaon/apps/KaonTftpService/
5. \vendor\kaon\prebuilts\bkouc500\KaonManagerService 의 apk 다른 폴더에 복사해 놓기 
5-1. KaonHiddenMenu 디렉토리 원복 
6.  vendor/kaon/Android.mk  원복 
7. ./bcm.ref.sh -d K1100UA_bkouc500 -o > 빌드 실패 
8. git stash 
9. apk 원래 폴더에 덮어쓰기 
10. /bcm.ref.sh -d K1100UA_bkouc500 -o 
mmm vendor/kaon/apps/KaonCmAutoUpgrade/ 

히든메뉴 빌드방법 
1. 다운로드 
$ cd ./vendor/kaon/apps 
$ git clone git@kkms.kaonmedia.com:hcn/apps.git 

2. build 
$ cd (source root) 
$ ./bcm.ref.sh -d K1100UA_bkouc500 

3. 결과물 
./out/target/product/K1100UA/system/priv-app/HiddenMenu/HiddenMenu.apk 
./out/target/product/K1100UA/system/lib/libhiddenmenu.so 
./out/target/product/K1100UA/system/lib/libhiddenmenu_jni.so 

4. prebuilt에 적용 
cp -f ./out/target/product/K1100UA/system/priv-app/HiddenMenu/HiddenMenu.apk ./vendor/kaon/prebuilts/bkouc500/KaonHiddenMenu/HiddenMenu/ 
cp -f ./out/target/product/K1100UA/system/lib/libhiddenmenu.so ./vendor/kaon/prebuilts/bkouc500/KaonHiddenMenu/HiddenMenuService/ 
cp -f ./out/target/product/K1100UA/system/lib/libhiddenmenu_jni.so ./vendor/kaon/prebuilts/bkouc500/KaonHiddenMenu/HiddenMenu_JNI/ 




