[‎2024-‎06-‎25 오전11:18]  김원균[KIM WONKYUN]:  
If there are nexus API changes, you have to do "ioctl exporting" by -x option, then rebuild it. ioctl_xxx files will be updated in your platform folder.
<Example of updating ioctl with inuvik platform>
# ./bcm.bdst.nxl.sh -d inuvik -x
$ find device/broadcom/inuvik -name "ioctl_*" 
device/broadcom/inuvik/sepolicy/treble/cli/ioctl_macros
device/broadcom/inuvik/sepolicy/treble/cli/ioctl_defines
device/broadcom/inuvik/sepolicy/treble/enc/ioctl_macros
device/broadcom/inuvik/sepolicy/treble/enc/ioctl_defines
device/broadcom/inuvik/sepolicy/treble/nvk/ioctl_macros
device/broadcom/inuvik/sepolicy/treble/nvk/ioctl_defines 


